Class QueueHandler

java.lang.Object
  QueueHandler

public class QueueHandler
extends java.lang.Object

QueueHandler class has one major purpose, to manage all the queues and instances of the ObjectQueue class It creates 5 queue Objects, Jobqueue, Q1, Q2, Q3, and Q4

Version:
Final 4/6/2018
Author:
Eric Davey
